data.name: invite_subject
data.value: Write to me with ECSMail, the next-generation e-mail program!

data.name: invite_text
data.value: Hi,{0}{0}I don't want Google to read my e-mail anymore, so I installed ECS support into my mail programs and I invite you to do the same. Besides protecting our privacy, the ECS products from ChiaraMail help protect us from email spoofing, in which others try to trick us into revealing our bank login credentials and such, and also enable us to change our e-mail after we've sent it (Yes! Really!). As if that weren't enough, ECS technology allows us to send attachments of practically unlimited size and also speeds up mail delivery, while greatly reducing mail storage requirements for our mail recipients.{0}{0}I think ECS is a big deal and wanted to share the news about it with you. If you have an Android phone or tablet, download ECSMail for Android from https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.chiaramail.chiaramailforandroid. For Mozilla Thunderbird or Microsoft Outlook users, download free extensions from http://www.chiaramail.com/download_extension.html and take control of your e-mail today like I did!{0}{0}Regards,{0}{0}{1}
